{"tid":342704,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「請先讓車上乘客落車 多謝合作」","createTime":"2017-07-31T22:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T13:29:28.000Z","uid":8830,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa435e75e1ddfc71afbb5ef4ab3c84761384529","tid":342704,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T22:38:10.000Z","msg":"地鐵黃衫波板糖人&mdash;地鐵精心設計的一個鬧鐘<br />\n<br />\n早上八時半，地鐵站無數的打工仔，內心不約而同地說著同一句說話&mdash;「好眼訓呀」。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，一群專業、熱心服務的黃衫軍正以友善、和藹可親的態度，喚醒等車的打工仔。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「請先讓車上乘客落車，然後上車，多謝合作」<br />\n「上左車既乘客請盡量行入車箱中間，多謝合作」<br />\n「上唔到車既乘客請返回黃線後面等車」<br />\n「攜帶大型行李既乘客請使用升降機」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n也許你內心會質疑：<br />\n為何提醒別人排隊和小心空隙要以這麼大的音量<br />\n為何對乘客講話要用對殺父仇人的聲線和態度<br />\n為何一句多謝合作是那麼的虛偽<br />\n為何建議變了命令<br />\n為何對插隊的內地旅客和長者視若無睹<br />\n等等等等等等<br />\n<br />\n讓我告訴你，他們是地鐵公司重金禮聘，維持打工仔精神的專業團隊。試比較一下家中的鬧鐘和黃衫軍的吵鬧聲線，顯然是高下立見。地鐵公司深明此道理，訓練出一群專業鬧鐘團隊，目的是以高分具音波炮，喚醒沉睡的打工仔，維持社會正常運作，為香港建立更佳的國際金融中心形象。<br />\n<br />\n完成一天辛勞的工作，你仍然會看見黃衫軍繼續努力以音波炮<del>進行攻擊</del>喚睡市民。咦？工作時間不是過了嗎？他們只想提醒你，家中仍然是辦公室，只需一封電郵、一個來電、一個訊息。家中頓時演變成辦公室。即使離開了工作崗位，你必須打醒十二分精神，緊記你的時間是公司的資產。<br />\n<br />\n每日辛勞工作，乘車時更有專業的鬧鐘團隊為打工仔打打氣，每一次聽到他們使出音波絕招，我只擔心身心俱疲的打工仔，把他們的說話內容變成.........<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「由於大圍站發生墮軌意外，本班車將稍為延遲」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n他們不再是鬧鐘，而是這個都市的喪鐘。<br />\n<br />\n筆者在此感激各位<del>嘈撚到仆街的</del>黃衫軍。"},{"pid":"4cfda4ca0f1b1b4641ecf6c085b1ae7eafd58c80","tid":342704,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T22:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43319e21419f09cdac509013c78f508f41393d65","tid":342704,"uid":17684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T22:47:18.000Z","msg":"正評。班友（尤其c9果d）真係煩到想叫佢收聲。人肉錄音機咁。請咁多黃衫燃，減價好過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42987c5415fdd84b64009fb7e01ff001b75a8b97","tid":342704,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T22:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評。班友（尤其c9果d）真係煩到想叫佢收聲。人肉錄音機咁。請咁多黃衫燃，減價好過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前都係舉個牌 <br />\n禁個會響既東西提你唔好過黃線/衝門<br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deab6157798a5e5929d7f7b18fc047ab1bdf9a83","tid":342704,"uid":130613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:30:35.000Z","msg":"其實佢地都係機械式<br />\n無表情 無情緒<br />\n只想嗌到快d收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b46709742a450a7447dfbb0b212e425a24013a","tid":342704,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:34:23.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d82e480ec7e31f0f677bf2b3eba0b4546618753","tid":342704,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa80f00afff1acab9e2fa108049c0afb8a555ea","tid":342704,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢地都係機械式<br />\n無表情 無情緒<br />\n只想嗌到快d收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55b51e484efe45e1a25f7e3f65dc3f60e438682","tid":342704,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T03:06:48.000Z","msg":"「上左車既乘客請盡量行入車箱中間，多謝合作」<br />\n<br />\n香港仲有好多人未上車<br />\n所以唔行入車箱中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739096cc2dabc8ba41313bea25543df9976f30ab","tid":342704,"uid":76787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"啲撚屌識聽就唔撚洗咁嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未撚落完車就沖上車<br />\n上車企正門口<br />\n拖喼又唔撚搭lift<br />\n啲廢老又sip位又唔撚識睇箭咀on99<br />\n諗起都把幾火"},{"pid":"f2d4784867f9b34b381501d2e6566bef4d2cf0fa","tid":342704,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"渣過地鐵就明冇班minions<br />\n繁忙時間閂門會搞勁耐<br />\n然後高層就會屌鳩你delay no more<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申已quit"},{"pid":"36a352b86245b88acf94a0e6546488e9cb133b8e","tid":342704,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲撚屌識聽就唔撚洗咁嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未撚落完車就沖上車<br />\n上車企正門口<br />\n拖喼又唔撚搭lift<br />\n啲廢老又sip位又唔撚識睇箭咀on99<br />\n諗起都把幾火</blockquote><br />\n每次都同廢老進行激烈既身體碰撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd12d7c0e785dd9066810c87aae49edb411eb49","tid":342704,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82414d4ff7e80794c35a982070b635804fbe563","tid":3427